{"tid":2194671,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大公共衞生學院教授高本恩回應林鄭「所謂專家醫生」抹黑論：政府基本責任是確保公帑用得其所","createTime":"2020-09-08T15:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T16:47:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a08dec427609db22e1144aba172423e344c727d9","tid":2194671,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:48:09.000Z","msg":"全民自願檢測計劃受專家質疑成效，香港大學公共衞生學院教授高本恩，接受電視節目「清心直說」訪問時表示，自己未有參與全民自願檢測，認為計劃花費巨額公帑，相信有市民認為計劃是浪費公帑，及涉及政治原因而不參加。<br />\n<br />\n對於特首林鄭月娥早前批評「所謂專家醫生」抹黑檢測計劃，高本恩表示，很奇怪有政府官員不認為計劃需要考慮成本效益，任何政府的基本責任是確保公帑用得其所，計算成本效益是決定善用公帑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/CZ6LJIFYBFDCBBQIYF3UY5J734/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FCZ6LJIFYBFDCBBQIYF3UY5J734%2F&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=9b401c62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FCZ6LJIFYBFDCBBQIYF3UY5J734%2F&h=d2ba7530\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/CZ6LJIFYBFDCBBQIYF3UY5J734/</a>"},{"pid":"92ad04068d91725f1909634e42e947fbf4196987","tid":2194671,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe818051c8df5c73751a51adbeb48ed60e68783","tid":2194671,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92ad04068d91725f1909634e42e947fbf4196987","tid":2194671,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T15:50:11.000